 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/9a3cbe05-786b-43f4-a932-f43483d39aca-ezgif.com-gif-to-webp-converter_3000x3000.webp?v=1756237059" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="450" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996388" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996388"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Wenn ich an die schönsten Momente meines Lebens denke, dann sind viele davon mit unserer Katze Mimi verbunden. Sie war 14 Jahre lang Teil unserer Familie – verspielt, verschmust und voller Persönlichkeit.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jedes Mal, wenn ich nach Hause kam, begrüßte sie mich mit ihrem typischen leisen Schnurren. Ihre glänzenden Augen funkelten, als wollte sie sagen: „Da bist du ja endlich.“ Und wenn ich traurig war, kuschelte sie sich an mich und schenkte mir Wärme – ohne ein Wort, aber mit so viel Liebe.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1714045396277" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1714045396277" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/825dad7f-a654-45fe-bfe5-091511319adf/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/6.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1719233200833" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1719233200833" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Und dann kam ein Geschenk, das alles veränderte…</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1752062029176" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1752062029176"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Es war ein gemütlicher Sonntag. Meine Tochter brachte mir ein kleines Päckchen. Ich sah sofort, dass es mit viel Liebe verpackt war.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Als ich es öffnete, blieb mir der Atem weg:</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000">Ein handgemachtes 3D Holz-Puzzle in Katzenform.</font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="